</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>《Gran Turismo 7》實體版，即日起開放預訂</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/01/07/gran-turismo-7-pre-order/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=gran-turismo-7-pre-order</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[唐美鳳]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jan 2022 02:03:22 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[遊戲情報]]></category><category><![CDATA[Gran Turismo 7]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1079967</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>相信不少 PS4 和 PS5 機迷，還有喜歡模擬駕駛的車迷們，都在期待著遊戲《Gran Turismo 7》的推出，昨日 PlayStation HK 終於宣佈，由即日（1 月 7 日起）起接受遊戲實體版的預訂，無論預訂任何版本，都會獲得遊戲內道具和車款包。</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>相信不少 PS4 和 PS5 機迷，還有喜歡模擬駕駛的車迷們，都在期待著遊戲《Gran Turismo 7》的推出，昨日 PlayStation HK 終於宣佈，由即日（1 月 7 日起）起接受遊戲實體版的預訂，無論預訂任何版本，都會獲得遊戲內道具和車款包。</p><p><span id="more-1079967"></span></p><p><a href="https://unwire.hk/2022/01/09/our-next-energy-tests-its-750-mile-range-prototype-in-a-tesla-model-s/life-tech/auto/attachment/0107-2b-3/" rel="attachment wp-att-1080002"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1080002" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/0107-2b-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/0107-2b-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/0107-2b-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/0107-2b.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>成功預訂《Gran Turismo 7》任何版本，都可以獲得遊戲內貨幣 100,000CR，還有包括 MAZDA RX-VISION GT3 CONCEPT Stealth Model、Porsche 917 LIVING LEGEND ’14 和 Toyota Supra GT500 ’97 (Castrol TOM’S) 的車款包。此外，預購指定實體版本還可以獲得預購特典，包括金屬皮革鑰匙圈或賽道杯墊。</p><p><a href="https://unwire.hk/2022/01/09/our-next-energy-tests-its-750-mile-range-prototype-in-a-tesla-model-s/life-tech/auto/attachment/0107-2c/" rel="attachment wp-att-1080001"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1080001" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/0107-2c-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/0107-2c-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/0107-2c-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/0107-2c.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>這款《Gran Turismo》系列 25 週年的作品，將會同時推出 PS4 和 PS5 版本，並且會在今年 3 月 4 日正式推出，普通版和 25 週年紀念版均會有實體和數位版，分別透過零售店和 PS Store 發售。</p><p><a href="https://unwire.hk/2022/01/09/our-next-energy-tests-its-750-mile-range-prototype-in-a-tesla-model-s/life-tech/auto/attachment/0107-2d/" rel="attachment wp-att-1080000"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1080000" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/0107-2d-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/0107-2d-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/0107-2d-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/0107-2d.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>來源：<a href="https://blog.zh-hant.playstation.com/2022/01/06/20220106-gt7/">playstation</a></p>
