方罰款 6000 元人民幣（約港幣 7341 元）。公子沈其後在影片中表示，這個小粉紅（該名中國網民）應該是在舉報時留下實名信息，所以讓網警以非法翻牆為由處罰。</span></p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_64448"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/6t-wGunnD64?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">公子沈又透露，自己因為對方的辱罵言論向 Twitter 檢舉，該名中國網民的帳號現已被封鎖。公子沈笑稱，有點後悔沒把「小粉紅」的奇文留下來，讓大家共賞一番。</span></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="zh" dir="ltr">舉報我，他被罰款；被我舉報，他又被封號。小粉紅不解：「親愛的祖國和萬惡的反華分子難道是一夥的？怎麼都在對付我們這些愛國群眾？」🤣🤣🤣 <a href="https://t.co/JsBIl63h9b">pic.twitter.com/JsBIl63h9b</a></p><p>&mdash; 公子沈 Mr. Shen (@Terenceshen) <a href="https://twitter.com/Terenceshen/status/1478139652234219520?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">January 3, 2022</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：</span><a href="https://youtu.be/6t-wGunnD64"><span style="font-weight: 400;">YouTube</span></a></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 :</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
